commands to pass according to environmemts

$ terraform apply -var-file "dev.tfvars"  -auto-approve      ( to create resource )

$ terraform destroy -var-file "dev.tfvars"  -auto-approve    (to destroy resource )


note :  IF YOU OBSERVE THE ABOVE COMMANDS WE CAN SEE "dev.tfvars" so that we can pass the arguments through commandline for desired environment we want at the time 
        of EXECUTION
